Subject:      CHAIN #2
 
Now available:
Chain/2: Documentary
Edited by Jena Osman and Juliana Spahr
 
The second issue of Chain questions the supposed neutrality/objectivity of
documentary forms. The concerns of this issue are: in what ways does the
topical world filter through language? how do creative forms actually capture
an event, a person, a place? The work included highlights the way we use
language/image to cut up our experiential encounters so as to (re)see them.
 
Contributing writers and artists: Alicia Askenase, Lutz Bacher, Merle Lyn
Bachman, Dodie Bellamy, Celia Bland, Pascale-Anne Brault, Sherry Brennan,
