You wrote:
>
> forgive my ignorance: who are the Oulipians?--maria damon
>
The Society for Potential Literature, a wonderful internationalist
literary "school" out of Europe -- Jacques Roubaud (whose name I may be
misspelling), Georges Perec, Italo Calvino and Harry Matthews have all
been associated with this phenomenon.
