Chris S. -- found your nearly immediate move from interesting remark re:
lyric to a radical narrowing of the question to just a few forms of music
odd -- and the opposition even odder, as most poets & critics of my
acquaintance (an admittedly unrepresentative sampling) seem, if anything,
