From:         "Aldon L. Nielsen" <anielsen@SPARTA.SJSU.EDU>
Subject:      Re: Nothing
In-Reply-To:  <9505120719.AA20258@isc.sjsu.edu>
 
Here we go again, to paraphrase our memoriuos ex-president, Ronald X.
 
Please!  Before anyone again refers to the notoripus"nothing outside the
text" line, go read Michael Berube's discussion of the translation of
that line in his book _Public Access_, (Verso eds.)
 
For a long list of philosophers who have had something to say about
nothing, see the Encyclopedia of Philosophy, where nothing is summed up
rather nicely.
 
Ed, is Derrida still outside your old house, or did he follow along to
the outside of your new place?
