Writing between the Lines: Race and Intertextuality.  pub'd last Summer
by U of Georgia Press at an unconscionable price (but cheaper than Alan's
hardback!) -- not yet in paper so look for it in the library at your
nearest college. -- next one will be in simultaneous paper & cloth from
Cambridge,, next year.
 
